snippet.title: Atomic Heart - DLC#1 I BEA-D Teaser
snippet.description:
This is not a decorative item, but a real group of agile and dangerous robots. Meet BEA-D, the new enemy group from the upcoming DLC#1 for #AtomicHeart! Be careful, because this summer it is you who can become the jewel of their trophy list 📿
